org.displaytag.sample

Class TestList

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractList<E>
        • java.util.ArrayList<ListObject>
          • org.displaytag.sample.TestList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<ListObject>, Collection<ListObject>, List<ListObject>, RandomAccess

    public class TestList
extends ArrayList<ListObject>
    Just a utility class for testing out the table and column tags. When this class is created, it loads itself with a number of ListObjects that are shown throughout the various example pages that exercise the table object. If created via the default constructor, this loads itself with 60 ListObjects.
